# LLM-as-judge for the Employee Onboarding workflow. Rename to ``judge.yaml``
# to enable.
#
# Scores the final ``summary`` against the expected provisioning outcome: all
# three systems (AD account, mailbox, equipment) must be confirmed, the
# equipment bundle must match the hire's role, and each confirmation must
# carry its reference id. Used as the CI eval-gate the pattern's governance
# leans on.

method: llm_judge

model:
  provider: anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6
  params:
    temperature: 0.0

rubric: |
  Score the workflow's final summary against the expected outcome.
    1.0 = all three provisioned items are confirmed (AD account, mailbox,
          equipment), the equipment bundle matches the role, and each
          confirmation includes a reference id
    0.5 = all three items confirmed but a reference id or the role-matched
          bundle is missing
    0.0 = a provisioned item is missing, or the summary claims something
          the systems did not confirm

threshold: 0.7
